outbreakTemplates.description:
Case investigation form for influenza outbreak investigations.
For detailed information about this template and guidance on completing the disease-specific reference data values, please refer to the data dictionary and/or the metadata overview available at: https://worldhealthorganization.github.io/godata/outbreak-templates/
